d=\"cite_note-Rtsotd.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtsotd.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtsotd.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\">4.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sons_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Sons of the Dragon\">The Sons of the Dragon</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n\n<tbody><tr style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<td style=\"width:30%;\" rowspan=\"1\">Preceded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/Alton_Celtigar\" title=\"Alton Celtigar\">Alton Celtigar</a></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>4th <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a> </b><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_17_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">17</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_34_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">34&#160;AC</a>        <br /><small>Served under: <b><a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a></b></small>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\">Succeeded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Stokeworth\" title=\"Alyn Stokeworth\">Alyn Stokeworth</a></div>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist mw-collapsible mw-collapsed collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=